		<td><b>Modern Mallard - Light gun and Duck Hunt mod for modern TVs</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Someone's running a kickstarter for this:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/metsasta/modern-mallard">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/me ... rn-mallard</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It replaces the light gun's sensor with one that can see a newer TV, and has a patch board for Duck Hunt to add more delay to its light tests to account for lag.<br /><br />The asking price is $129 though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


